title: Grateful Dead Live at Copps Coliseum on 1990-03-22
description:
Set I
Feel Like A Stranger
West L.A. Fadeaway
Easy To Love You
Beat It On Down The Line
It Must Have Been The Roses
The Last Time
Picasso Moon
Don't Ease Me In
Set II
Scarlet Begonias >
Fire On The Mountain
Samson & Delilah
Believe It Or Not >
Truckin' >
Drums >
Space >
The Other One >
Hey Jude >
Dear Mr. Fantasy >
Hey Jude >
Sugar Magnolia

Encore:
It's All Over Now Baby Blue

 
Comment
Jerry Garcia - Guitar
Bob Weir - Guitar
Brent Mydland - Keyboards
Phil Lesh - Bass
Bill Kreutzmann - Drums
Mickey Hart - Drums
